HAVE_UNISTD	DO
##  Do you have setbuffer?  Pick DO or DONT.
#### =()<HAVE_SETBUFFER		@<HAVE_SETBUFFER>@>()=
HAVE_SETBUFFER		DO
##  Do you have gettimeofday?  Pick DO or DONT.
